          "name": "NPC Core",
          "page": 140,
          "type": "source"
        }
      ],
      "text": "These world-wise scholars know that there's more to life than just research. There are also good meals at the university refectory, comfortable beds, and captive audiences of students.",
      "type": "section"
    }
  ],
